<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="secure-vt">secure <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sɪ'kjʊə(r)/    美 /sə'kjʊr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使安全；保证；获得：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>secure</strong> sb <strong>against</strong> / from attack 
保证某人不受袭击</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>secure a position in a firm 
在一家公司找到一个职位</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(尤指经过努力) 获得；取得</strong></h4>
<h4 id="3">3.<strong>使…固定：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He secured the rope firmly to the back of the car.
他把绳子牢牢地拴在车后。</p></div></div>